      "writtenOn": "2019-11-18T20:06:32Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "FWIW, I care much more about the top level field name than the contents. resultdb has good specificity for a top level key (since it refers to a concrete service/idea, more than just \"results\").\n\nThat said... \"resultdb/resultsink\" could maybe just be \"resultdb/sink\"? Unless you plan to have multiple sinks as part of resultdb?",
      "parentUuid": "5d0ce387_2d165cf4",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 29,
        "startChar": 5,
        "endLine": 29,
        "endChar": 16
      },
